Author_Bob_How_Year_4001So_I_suppose_its:
[Author: Bob How] [Year: 4001]
So I suppose it's not all doom and gloom here. It looks like the trees and plants here at least offer something in the way of resources.
Just setting a few clones on the trees for an hour yielded huge stacks of wood for us to use in manufacturing.
The plants work great as a fiber material too. It's surprising how well it performs when compare to Earthly materials.
